Package: fflr
Title: Query the ESPN Fantasy Football API
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kiernan",
           family = "Nicholls",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kiernann@protonmail.com")
Description: This package provides an R interface to the
    ESPN Fantasy Football API using the httr package for a backend.
    Programatic collection of statistics for both fantasy teams and
    individual players.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/kiernann/fflr
